front.title: •You Cannot Hide Forever
front.gametext: Deploy on table. Opponent's Jedi are defense value -1. Never Tell Me The Odds is canceled. You may place Effect in Lost Pile to take one [Endor] or [Death Star II] Effect that deploys for free into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: 'Give yourself to the dark side. It is the only way you can save your friends.'

pulls: One (Endor icon) or (Death Star II icon) Effect that deploys for free
